  m_text: "\u2022 You have a 2-second window to respond each time the finjal      
    \n   appears.\n\n\u2022 Press SPACE only when the falcon is above the cross.\n\n\u2022
    Do NOT press anything if the falcon is below the cross, doing \n   so will cost
    you one heart.\n\n\u2022 Stay focused and keep your hearts to reach a higher
    score."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8dd69308a8a1a194ba2eb977b596c01c, type: 2}
